routeFacts.name: Hauptstrecke Rhein-Ruhr
routeFacts.description: Hauptstrecke Rhein-Ruhr is a German route for Train Sim World featuring a 46 kilometre section of the Rhein-Ruhr S-Bahn between Duisburg and Bochum via Essen. It features the DB BR 425 and DB BR 422 EMUs.
routeInfo: The route covers a 46 kilometre section of the Rhein-Ruhr S-Bahn between Duisburg HBF and Bochum HBF via Essen. Between Essen and Bochum the route splits in to two. Featured with the route are the S1, S3, RE11 and RB33 services, whilst owners of selected other German content can drive freight services, as well as RE1, RE2 and RE6 services along the route.
